public interface Displayable
Interface for displaying all user interface elements. A Displayable represents a user interface element which can be displayed to the standard output.

This interface is implemented by base classes as generic user interface elements like SelectionMenu and Form. More specific user interface components are implemented by either extension from these base classes or association of these base classes.
